### Jazz Cash Payment API Tests

# Base URL for development
@baseUrl = https://localhost:5001/api/jazzcash
@contentType = application/json

### 1. Create Mobile Account Payment Request
POST {{baseUrl}}/create-payment
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "amount": 1000.00,
  "customerId": "customer123",
  "callbackUrl": "https://yourapp.com/payment-success"
}

### 2. Create Voucher Payment Request
POST {{baseUrl}}/create-voucher-payment
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "amount": 500.00,
  "customerId": "customer456",
  "mobileNumber": "03001234567"
}

### 3. Get Transaction Status
@transactionId = T20240925143022
GET {{baseUrl}}/transaction-status/{{transactionId}}

### 4. Refund Payment
POST {{baseUrl}}/refund
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "transactionId": "T20240925143022",
  "amount": 500.00
}

### 5. Void Transaction
POST {{baseUrl}}/void
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "transactionId": "T20240925143022"
}

### 6. Test Payment Callback (This would normally come from Jazz Cash)
POST {{baseUrl}}/callback
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

pp_TxnRefNo=T20240925143022&pp_ResponseCode=000&pp_ResponseMessage=Transaction completed successfully&pp_Amount=100000&pp_TxnCurrency=PKR&pp_SecureHash=test-hash

